<item>
            <title>[JAMES-2107] Java 8 Migration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JAMES-2107</link>
                <project id="10411" key="JAMES">James Server</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This migration can be split into several substeps:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Merge the java-6 and java-8 compilation Dockerfiles (and adapt CI)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Upgrade targetted JDK and correct problems&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Simplify Java-8 poms (remove profiles)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Upgrade dependencies that were wanted but not doable in java-6 (camel, Artemis, activeMQ, etc...)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Limit the usage of Guava (FluentIterables and the like, Optional, Objects, etc...) and replace it with Java-8 classes&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Apply automatic IntelliJ refactoring to migrate to Java-8&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
